reviewText: All three dvd's were in perfect condition and just as good as I had remembered them.

Great threesome! I gave it 4 stars simply because Philadelphia was too much. Great movie, just a little to painful. It's more of a watch once type of movie. Great to watch, but no one wants to revisit that type of pain.

'A League Of Their Own' is a fantastic movie. I think I liked it more after I found out that the movie was about real women in a pro baseball league. I looked them up on the internet,  and they really were pro baseball players. I think they were great. I would like to go to the 'Baseball Hall Of Fame'  one day to at least to just see their pictures.
I love all three of these movies so this is a great deal for the price!  Don't hesitate to buy.

The wife and I are big Hanks fans and this was really a great deal getting 3 films for that price was really a good deal. The were well packaged, arrived timely and were without flaws. I would definitely shop with them again
I have enjoyed seeing all three on my new portable DVD player. They Do bring back old memories.  That is always a good thing.
Terrific price for 3 good movies. Basic flicks. No extras on the 'A League of TheirOwn'. Bought primarily for that movie, but I will enjoy watching the others as well.
